out of the picture.

20:36.104 --> 20:40.239
Which was your
objective, right?

20:40.282 --> 20:42.502
Oh, I've watched you
waste your potential

20:42.545 --> 20:45.592
year after year after year,

20:45.635 --> 20:48.290
wondering when you would
reach out and

20:48.334 --> 20:51.206
start taking what was
rightfully yours.

20:53.774 --> 20:55.254
How rewarding it must feel

20:55.297 --> 20:56.472
