she calls it off.

21:10.791 --> 21:12.096
- She.

21:12.140 --> 21:14.316
You really hired a woman
to do this, huh?

21:16.057 --> 21:18.842
Well, nobody's getting
in here, Miss Barbour.

21:18.886 --> 21:20.235
