21:22.411 --> 21:24.370
So what do you say?

21:24.413 --> 21:27.242
How about a tour?

21:27.286 --> 21:29.375
You've got nothing to worry
about, I can assure you.

21:29.418 --> 21:30.941
It's totally safe.

21:30.985 --> 21:32.639
And as a fellow
art history buff,

21:32.682 --> 21:33.944
I've got a few pieces
that I think

21:33.988 --> 21:37.252
you're really gonna love.

21:37.296 --> 21:38.732
Come on.

21:38.775 --> 21:42.257
After you.

21:43.780 --> 21:45.913
- Okay.

22:12.156 --> 22:13.244
- Miguel!

22:13.288 --> 22:15.986
