23:23.967 --> 23:26.970
Quick.
Quick.

23:27.014 --> 23:30.409
- I...

23:30.452 --> 23:31.845
Okay.

23:31.888 --> 23:32.846
- Quick, Pen.

23:32.889 --> 23:37.503
Go. Go, quick.

23:38.721 --> 23:40.201
- Time's up.

23:40.244 --> 23:41.985
Please exit
the Witch Tent now.

23:42.029 --> 23:44.988
Thank you.
