25:51.593 --> 25:53.247
Cost me 600 grand.

25:53.290 --> 25:54.944
- David, shouldn't we be...
- Yes. No, no, no, no.

25:54.988 --> 25:57.120
There's just one more thing
I'd like to show you.

25:57.164 --> 25:58.295
It's on the floor below.

25:58.339 --> 26:01.429
It's the
pièce de résistance.

26:01.472 --> 26:04.432
One of the finest collections
in the city.

26:04.475 --> 26:08.479
And also, there's a full bath
and private bedroom.

26:08.523 --> 26:11.482
And it's all yours
until the night is over.

26:11.526 --> 26:13.833
Consider it my apology
to you for

26:13.876 --> 26:16.183
