32:41.133 --> 32:42.699
Oh--oh--

32:48.488 --> 32:50.664
- Bitch put up
a hell of a fight.

32:50.707 --> 32:54.146
I'll give you that.

32:54.189 --> 32:56.278
- But you should never,
ever, ever

32:56.322 --> 32:59.673
hire a woman
to do a man's job.

33:01.066 --> 33:02.545
- Now, Miss Barbour,

33:02.589 --> 33:06.419
I'd love to show you
the rest of my collection.

33:09.117 --> 33:10.597
Right this way.

33:19.910 --> 33:21.782
- Look at you, beautiful.

33:21.825 --> 33:23.871
- Shh.

33:23.914 --> 33:24.915
- Mmm, mmm, mmm.

33:27.788 --> 33:29.050
- I don't want to hurt you.

33:29.094 --> 33:30.791
I just want to taste you.

33:30.834 --> 33:32.053
- Play nice.

33:33.750 --> 33:35.100
- You're soft.

33:35.143 --> 33:37.363
- It's a living,
breathing art gallery.

33:37.406 --> 33:39.060
You can look and touch
but nothing more.

33:39.104 --> 33:40.061
The rules are very strict.

33:40.105 --> 33:41.062
There's no penetration,

33:41.106 --> 33:42.890
no nudity,

33:42.933 --> 33:45.936
and everything happens
over the clothes.

33:45.980 --> 33:49.418
If all the ladies behave
and keep quiet,

33:49.462 --> 33:52.291
they all get to go home
in the morning.

33:52.334 --> 33:54.989
Jane, when my father
founded this company,

33:55.033 --> 33:57.383
times were...

33:57.426 --> 33:59.167
simpler.

33:59.211 --> 34:01.343
Men were men, and.

34:01.387 --> 34:03.215
women were not.

34:03.258 --> 34:04.912
Then again, he

34:04.955 --> 34:07.784
lived by the motto
"No blacks, no broads," so...

34:07.828 --> 34:10.483
I'm sure you can appreciate
how far we've come.

34:10.526 --> 34:13.094
Thanks to a steady stream
of PC bullshit

34:13.138 --> 34:14.922
everything's become
a federal crime.

34:14.965 --> 34:16.924
I tell a woman I can't stop
thinking about her,

34:16.967 --> 34:18.969
she gets bent out of shape,
she runs to the Times,

34:19.013 --> 34:21.276
I lose my company.

34:21.320 --> 34:25.063
I've done nothing wrong and...

34:25.106 --> 34:27.108
my life is ruined.

34:27.152 --> 34:28.979
But not tonight, Jane.

34:29.023 --> 34:30.242
Not tonight.

34:30.285 --> 34:32.505
Tonight--

34:32.548 --> 34:34.724
tonight we don't have to
fight it.

34:34.768 --> 34:39.251
We can give in and become
the men that we once were.

34:39.294 --> 34:40.904
- Yeah.

34:45.170 --> 34:47.128
both: Here, here.

34:47.172 --> 34:48.869
- Anya here learned
how to play the game.

34:48.912 --> 34:53.047
Oh, yeah.

34:54.701 --> 34:59.836
- How do you think she got
the corner office?

34:59.880 --> 35:02.665
- You're pigs.

35:02.709 --> 35:04.276
Pigs.
This is disgusting.

35:04.319 --> 35:06.191
- Nobody's being killed here,
Miss Barbour.

35:06.234 --> 35:08.497
We're not, uh, animals.

35:08.541 --> 35:10.456
- We're human beings,

35:10.499 --> 35:14.286
Purging, as is our right
as Americans,

35:14.329 --> 35:15.287
as men.

35:15.330 --> 35:17.811
- You sick son of a bitch.

35:17.854 --> 35:20.466
I should have never, ever
tried to call it off.

35:20.509 --> 35:22.337
- But you did, you see.

35:22.381 --> 35:25.819
You did.

35:25.862 --> 35:29.866
And that's what makes you weak.

35:34.262 --> 35:36.046
♪

35:36.090 --> 35:37.439
- No!

35:37.483 --> 35:39.702
No!

35:39.746 --> 35:42.401
No!
