35:42.444 --> 35:43.402
No!

35:46.405 --> 35:48.276
- I've got an idea.

35:48.320 --> 35:51.061
Come on.

35:52.237 --> 35:54.630
- Hey, you.
Search over there.

35:54.674 --> 35:55.631
Take the left.

35:59.244 --> 36:01.768
- The cart's going to the tent.
Let's go.

36:03.422 --> 36:04.466
- There!

36:04.510 --> 36:06.468
