Get them!

36:06.512 --> 36:08.166
- Stop.

36:08.209 --> 36:09.167
Hands in the air.

36:09.210 --> 36:10.733
- Pen, here.

36:10.777 --> 36:11.865
- There they are!
- This way!

36:11.908 --> 36:13.432
- Throw this, now!

36:13.475 --> 36:14.868
- Put your hands up!
- Hands in the air.

36:22.092 --> 36:24.094
- Hey, go out that side!
Right there!

36:24.138 --> 36:25.705
- Hurry!

36:25.748 --> 36:29.056
- Stop. Hands in the air.

36:35.105 --> 36:38.108
- You're trapped, like
an animal locked in a cage.

36:38.152 --> 36:39.936
So what's the answer?

36:39.980 --> 36:42.069
Break free.
That's right.

36:42.112 --> 36:43.853
"Give me your tired,
your poor,

36:43.897 --> 36:46.029
your huddled masses
yearning to breathe free."

36:46.073 --> 36:49.859
That's on the
Statue of Liberty for a reason.

36:49.903 --> 36:54.255
Because she's America's
symbol of freedom.

36:54.299 --> 36:58.346
She holds a torch
to help us find our way.

36:58.390 --> 37:01.001
That's what I'm offering you.

37:01.044 --> 37:02.524
The torch.

37:02.568 --> 37:04.744
Now come and take it.

37:04.787 --> 37:07.094
Because we're all products
of our environment,

37:07.137 --> 37:09.836
our upbringing, our history.

37:09.879 --> 37:13.143
But the only way
to understand who you are

37:13.187 --> 37:15.711
is to recognize where
you came from.

37:16.930 --> 37:18.236
That's how you'll know what

37:18.279 --> 37:21.543
you're capable of becoming.

37:24.416 --> 37:26.200
♪

