37:35.775 --> 37:38.865
- Lila's dead.

37:39.996 --> 37:43.435
- Oh, my God.

37:43.478 --> 37:45.306
Jenna.

37:45.350 --> 37:47.613
I'm so sorry.

37:50.659 --> 37:52.400
♪

37:52.444 --> 37:56.099
About everything.

37:57.797 --> 38:01.104
God, this night--
this night is...

38:01.148 --> 38:03.063
- She knows what night it is.

38:03.106 --> 38:04.891
- Jenna...
- The baby knows.

38:04.934 --> 38:07.197
And she hates it.

38:07.241 --> 38:10.549
- She's just like her mom.

38:16.381 --> 38:20.689
You couldn't have saved Lila.
You know that. right?

38:20.733 --> 38:23.388
You tried but we barely
got out ourselves.

38:23.431 --> 38:29.307
And I know how awful
you must feel, but...

38:29.350 --> 38:32.222
I mean, come on, we have to
protect our family,

38:32.266 --> 38:35.051
no matter what.

38:35.095 --> 38:37.315
Come here.

38:37.358 --> 38:38.316
- Yeah.

38:41.014 --> 38:43.582
- It's okay.

38:53.635 --> 38:57.030
I'm hungry.

38:57.073 --> 38:59.728
Ah, Jesus,
how am I hungry again?

39:02.383 --> 39:04.777
Do you want me

39:04.820 --> 39:07.475
to make you some eggs?

39:07.519 --> 39:08.911
Okay.

39:08.955 --> 39:10.435
Do you mind if I ask her
if she would like to

39:10.478 --> 39:12.959
place an order for carryout?

39:13.002 --> 39:15.004
Yeah?

39:15.048 --> 39:19.444
One second.
- Okay.

39:23.230 --> 39:26.755
Hey, uh, your mom and I
were wondering

39:26.799 --> 39:30.759
if you would like
some scrambled eggs.

39:30.803 --> 39:34.284
- She says she would
like them over-easy.

39:35.634 --> 39:36.939
- With bacon.

39:36.983 --> 39:39.420
- Over-easy with bacon it is.

39:42.945 --> 39:44.947
You need anything else?

39:44.991 --> 39:47.515
- I just want tonight
to be over.

39:47.559 --> 39:49.561
- I know.
It almost is.

39:51.301 --> 39:52.477
Oh.

39:55.349 --> 39:57.003
Let's go eat.

40:01.050 --> 40:02.791
Don't worry,
they can't get inside.

40:05.098 --> 40:07.535
- Help! Help me!

40:07.579 --> 40:09.755
They're gonna kill me, please!

40:09.798 --> 40:11.147
Let me in, please!

40:11.191 --> 40:14.063
Please, help!

40:14.107 --> 40:17.197
Help! Please!

40:20.243 --> 40:27.250
♪
